COOSMEOCI

Commision Of OpenStreetMap Editors Of Central Iowa

What do we do?

We edit OSM (and Waze/GMaps/Ersi) for northern Polk County, southwestern Story County, and southeastern Boone County. We use a "minimapping" style, in which we will do house numbers, grass/forests, creeks, and buildings.

How do I join?

Contact Robert, and learn some OSM!
